oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Gerald Purcell and Associates Job No. 38421
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm); Arnold, Eddy, 1918-2008;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 2986) for an order placed by Gerald Purcell and Associates for 200 one color window cards for a performance by Eddie Arnold at the Madison County Coliseum in Huntsville, Alabama on June 17. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
